statements.sql: select * from "m_haigo_key" inner join "m_code" on "m_code"."kbn" = "m_haigo_key"."seihin_kbn" and "m_code"."code" = 'K51' and "m_code"."del_flg" = false where ("m_haigo_key"."haigo_key" = 'pS90R' and "m_haigo_key"."del_flg" = 0) limit 1

select "m_haigo_key_mei"."haigo_key", "m_haigo_key_mei"."hin_cd", "m_haigo_key_mei"."kikaku_cd", "m_haigo_key_mei"."ganryo_kbn", "m_haigo_key_mei"."bihikuru_keisu", "m_haigo_key_mei"."tonyu_group_no", "m_haigo_key_mei"."disp_jun", "K19"."name" as "K19", "C112"."name" as "C112", "K17"."name" as "K17", "C113"."name" as "C113", "C114"."name" as "C114", "C115"."name" as "C115" from "m_haigo_key_mei" inner join "m_kikaku" on "m_kikaku"."kikaku_cd" = "m_haigo_key_mei"."kikaku_cd" inner join "m_hinmoku_kikaku" on "m_hinmoku_kikaku"."kikaku_cd" = "m_kikaku"."kikaku_cd" and "m_hinmoku_kikaku"."hin_cd" = '00000001' and "m_hinmoku_kikaku"."del_flg" = false left join "m_code" as "K19" on "K19"."code" = 'K19' and "K19"."kbn" = "m_kikaku"."tuya_kbn" and "K19"."del_flg" = false left join "m_code" as "C112" on "C112"."code" = '112' and "C112"."kbn" = "m_kikaku"."irime_kbn" and "C112"."del_flg" = false left join "m_code" as "K17" on "K17"."code" = 'K17' and "K17"."kbn" = "m_kikaku"."irime_tani_kbn" and "K17"."del_flg" = false left join "m_code" as "C113" on "C113"."code" = '113' and "C113"."kbn" = "m_kikaku"."size_kbn" and "C113"."del_flg" = false left join "m_code" as "C114" on "C114"."code" = '114' and "C114"."kbn" = "m_kikaku"."kejyo_kbn" and "C114"."del_flg" = false left join "m_code" as "C115" on "C115"."code" = '115' and "C115"."kbn" = "m_kikaku"."meji_kbn" and "C115"."del_flg" = false where ("m_haigo_key_mei"."haigo_key" = 'pS90R' and "m_haigo_key_mei"."del_flg" = 0 and "m_haigo_key_mei"."kikaku_cd" = '1' and "m_haigo_key_mei"."hin_cd" = '00000001') limit 1
